title: Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office, US Congressional Districts, Oregon, 1990
name: Oregon Geospatial Enterprise Office, US Congressional Districts, Oregon, 1990
description:
This coverage shows the Oregon Congressional districts.
    This dataset was created to delineate Oregon Congressional districts for mapping purposes only. The coverage only delineates Congressional districts as they were drawn up by the Oregon Legislature for the 1990s.
